    %h2.heading
      Pitch Awesome
      %span.date
        \- (iOS, Swift, Audacity)
        \- October, 2015 - 
        %a{href: "http://bit.ly/pitch_awesome", target: "_blank"}<
          app
        \-
        %a{href: "https://github.com/Xavdidtheshadow/pitch_awesome/blob/master/README.md", target:"_blank"}
