    %h2.heading
      Quidditch API
      %span.date
        \- (nodejs, express, mongoose, mongo, mocha)
        \- June, 2015 - 
        %a{href: "https://quidapi.herokuapp.com", target: "_blank"}<
          site
        \-
        %a{href: "https://github.com/quidtech/quid_api", target:"_blank"}
